parameters.name: Mapped_Plasmapause_Grid_flip_vert
parameters.description: Sharpest gradient from equatorial IMAGE EUV Ion Images. Images flipped so 6MLT is to the left. This variable is a 'virtual' variable that is computed using the function alternate_view_flip_vert (see https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/pub/software/cdawlib/source/virtual_funcs.pro) on the with inputs of the variables ['Mapped_Plasmapause_Grid']. Note that some COMPONENTS may not be available from the HAPI interface. They are accessible from the raw CDF files, however.
parameters.x_cdf_FIELDNAM: Sharpest gradient from equatorial IMAGE EUV !CIon Images. 12MLT=down, 6MLT=left
